{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2096566, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "“听说”", "timestamp": 1626687253, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096567, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你觉得“外国的月亮”合适吗😅😅😅", "timestamp": 1626687266, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096570, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "加拿大就是。", "timestamp": 1626687289, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096573, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "😓这种公诉刑事案件不按照疑罪重无才是奇怪吧", "timestamp": 1626687304, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096575, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我惊呆了", "timestamp": 1626687304, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096584, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "疑罪从无才符合法治规范嘛。", "timestamp": 1626687336, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096588, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这种案件女方举证很复杂，很多强j案都不了了之", "timestamp": 1626687353, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096592, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "而且应该是公安负责举证吧", "timestamp": 1626687384, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096593, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在中国，所有的罪的判断，没有一个是要求被告人自证清白的。这才叫好的法治。", "timestamp": 1626687391, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096596, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "首先，公诉罪的举证责任在公安和检察院，当然立案审查另算", "timestamp": 1626687413, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096600, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "加拿大其他类型案件适用于疑罪从无，但是强j案需要男方举证", "timestamp": 1626687441, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096606, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "但是确实应该是疑罪从无，这是法律法治的原则", "timestamp": 1626687469, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096607, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": 2096600, "tag": null, "text": "“这种罪行要特殊处理”，这种规则听起来就很奇怪吧。", "timestamp": 1626687480, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096612, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "疑罪从无这一点是有普适性的", "timestamp": 1626687521, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096619, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "其次，证据规则以举证责任倒置为例外，通常是针对实力地位相差悬殊的主体才会有这种特别保护。你想想男性和女性符不符合这个原则？", "timestamp": 1626687551, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096633, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "就连“证据有疑的要做对嫌疑人有利的推断”这么基础的刑法原则都要打补丁，这种法治想想就好奇怪。", "timestamp": 1626687632, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096657, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在我国，民事、行政的法律问题上有一些举证责任倒置的情形，主要是因为在这些情形，原告方面处于显著弱势地位、举证有显著困难。刑法搞这个是绝对不公正的。", "timestamp": 1626687909, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096666, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": 2096593, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 抛开现实问题同意你的说法，但例外是有的，巨额财产来源不明罪需要自证清白", "timestamp": 1626687965, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096700, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "需要举证对方同意就离谱，在这样的国家，每次上床前是不是都要签个同意书", "timestamp": 1626688171, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2096855, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": 2096666, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 这也不是疑罪从有啊，巨额财产本身也是证据啊", "timestamp": 1626689742, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2098024, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 407853, "reply_to": 2096855, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 指控的不是你有巨额财产，指控的是财产来源不明，你需要自己证明来源是清白的", "timestamp": 1626703959, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 407853, "reply": 21, "tag": null, "text": "听说中国这边告强j只能是女方举证，某些国家是是男方举证对方同意？？\n这又是外国的月亮更圆了吗", "timestamp": 1626687175, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1626703959, "url": "", "vote": {}}}